Abdulrasheed Maina, former Chairman of the Pension Reform Task Team (PRTT) is on his way back to Nigeria after been extradited from Niger Republic. SaharaReporters gathered that a team of police officers led by head of Interpol were in Niger Republic to pick Maina earlier on Thursday. File Photo: Abdulrasheed Maina The former PRTT Chairman is being prosecuted by the Economic and Financial Crimes Commission (EFCC) for alleged money laundering to the tune of N2 billion. See Also






